OL,3,CFather's campaign after finding wife
OL,4,Cdead at home
OL,6,FA father-of-two who found his wife
OL,7,Fdead at home aged just 31 is calling
OL,8,Ffor heart screening to be made more
OL,9,Froutinely available.
OL,11,FDale Lockwood returned from work as a
OL,12,Fprimary school deputy head teacher to
OL,13,Ffind his wife, Ruby, lifeless in bed
OL,14,Fat their home in Birstall, West
OL,15,FYorkshire.
OL,17,FIt was later found she had suffered
OL,18,Fsudden arrhythmic death syndrome, or
OL,19,FSADS, caused by a cardiac arrest with
OL,20,Fno clear cause.
