OL,3,CFather's campaign after finding wife
OL,4,Cdead at home
OL,6,FShe had worked as a detective for West
OL,7,FYorkshire Police and had been fit and
OL,8,Fhealthy until her death.
OL,10,FMr Lockwood, 33, is now campaigning
OL,11,Ffor ECG heart tests to be made
OL,12,Favailable to all under-18s.
OL,14,FHe said: "The condition Ruby had, nine
OL,15,Ftimes out of 10 can be identified with
OL,16,Fan ECG, which took five minutes.
OL,18,F"It's too late for us but if something
OL,19,Fcan be implemented to introduce an ECG
OL,20,Fit might save someone else."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
