OL,3,CFather's campaign after finding wife
OL,4,Cdead at home
OL,6,FMr Lockwood had last seen his wife on
OL,7,Fthe morning of her death after she
OL,8,Freturned from a night shift.
OL,10,FThey shared a cup of tea together
OL,11,Fbefore he left for work.
OL,13,FHe said he was extremely grateful for
OL,14,Fthose last moments together.
OL,16,F"I honestly can't remember the last
OL,17,Ftime we'd had that time, having two
OL,18,Fyoung children," he said.
OL,20,FHe said her last words to him were "I
OL,21,Flove you".
