OL,3,CFather's campaign after finding wife
OL,4,Cdead at home
OL,6,FSADS impacts around 500 people in the
OL,7,FUK every year.
OL,9,FAfter contacting the British Heart
OL,10,FFoundation, Mr Lockwood learned of the
OL,11,Fpotential genetic traits of the
OL,12,Fcondition and the increased chances of
OL,13,Fhis children also being carriers.
OL,15,FHe said: "If I hadn't done that my
OL,16,Fchildren could have been living with a
OL,17,Fticking time bomb".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
