OL,3,CFather's campaign after finding wife
OL,4,Cdead at home
OL,6,FMr Lockwood has raised more than
OL,7,F#19,000 for the British Heart
OL,8,FFoundation, recently taking part in
OL,9,Fthe Great North Run - the same event
OL,10,Fhis late wife ran in 2015 - to support
OL,11,Fgenetic testing.
OL,13,FHe said: "Ruby spent her whole life
OL,14,Fand work career helping people so I
OL,15,Ffeel I have got to do something
OL,16,Fbecause that's what Ruby would do."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
