OL,6,FEmily McGrath, senior cardiac nurse
OL,7,Ffor the BHF, said: "If you know what
OL,8,Fthe gene faults are it's easier to
OL,9,Fdiagnose people with these conditions.
OL,10,FIt also can potentially effect their
OL,11,Ffuture treatment options."
